OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1776967870
OL,3,CMan arrested at airport on suspicion
OL,4,Cof murdering Ellis Cox
OL,6,FA man has been arrested on suspicion
OL,7,Fof the murder of teenager Ellis Cox.
OL,9,FThe 19-year-old from Maghull was
OL,10,Fdetained at Liverpool John Lennon
OL,11,FAirport on 23 April , having arrived
OL,12,Fon a flight from Spain.
OL,14,FEllis, 19, was fatally shot at the
OL,15,FLiver Industrial Estate in Merseyside
OL,16,Fon 23 June 2024 when returning home
OL,17,Ffrom a bike ride, and the
OL,18,Finvestigation into his death is
OL,19,Fongoing.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/3
