FL,395,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1776967870
OL,3,CMan arrested at airport on suspicion
OL,4,Cof murdering Ellis Cox
OL,6,FHe is the seventh person to be
OL,7,Farrested in connection with this case,
OL,8,Fwith six people who were previously
OL,9,Farrested all on conditional bail
OL,10,Fpending further inquiries.
OL,12,FDetective Chief Inspector Steve
OL,13,FMcGrath said: "I hope this latest
OL,14,Farrest shows how our investigation
OL,15,Fteam remain as determined as ever to
OL,16,Fget justice for Ellis' family and time
OL,17,Fis no barrier to our relentless
OL,18,Fpursuit of all those involved in his
OL,19,Fmurder.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/3
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,395,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1776967870
OL,3,CMan arrested at airport on suspicion
OL,4,Cof murdering Ellis Cox
OL,6,F"Although we have now made another
OL,7,Farrest in connection with this
OL,8,Fincident, I want to urge anyone with
OL,9,Finformation to come forward.
OL,11,F"It has been nearly two years since
OL,12,FEllis was shot at the Liver Industrial
OL,13,FEstate and his family have been forced
OL,14,Fto live without anyone facing justice.
OL,16,F"If you have any information
OL,17,Fwhatsoever, please search your
OL,18,Fconscience and come forward. The
OL,19,Fsmallest detail could be vital to our
OL,20,Finquiries."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/3
